data.description: Beautiful end unit townhome in Crowell Farms. Primary bedroom and bath on main level with walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a bonus room/office on the second floor. Two car attached garage, covered front porch, rear patio and fully fenced rear yard. Cathedral ceiling in the living room with gas fireplace. Recent updates include new flooring throughout the majority of the home, interior paint, updated primary bath with new vanity and tiled shower and updated half bath, new gas furnace in past 2 years and new ac unit in past 5-6 years. Low HOA dues that provide for exterior maintenance and yard maintenance.
